title: WhiteHousePro - PageLines - Premium Wordpress Theme
description:
WhiteHousePro - A Premium Wordpress Theme by PageLines



-- Feature-Page Templates

Communicate with your customers clearly using the easy-to-use feature and highlight page templates.


-- New WP 3.0 Menus
The themes now support the new WordPress 3.0 menus. Drop-downs and multi-tier nav included.


-- Multiple Color Schemes
This theme has five color scheme options so you can pick the one that meets your needs.


-- Options and Flexibility
This theme has tons of options for you! It supports widgets, tons of plugins and custom CSS.


-- Pro Layout, Pro Design
Design is fundamental on the web, that's why this theme pays attention to details that create a professional impression.


-- Marketing & SEO
Reach or find new customers through the PageLines marketing framework and SEO-tuned theme markup.
